"""overview — Context-aware project overview tool for the Orin Nano hub.

Generates deep, per-project context views by combining live SSH probes,
LLM-powered CLAUDE.md extraction via Ollama on AGX, and rich ANSI rendering.

Usage:
    overview                        All projects summary (compact view)
    overview myproject              Deep view of a specific project
    overview myproject --refresh    Force re-analysis (bypass cache)
    overview myproject --raw        Show raw LLM JSON (debug)
    overview --refresh              Force re-analysis for all projects
"""

